[p 
	"A mysterious war, known as "The Havoc", has almost destroyed the human civilization. How it broke out is unknown, and no one even dare to study about it. The few survivers have to struggle for life, among whom our young hero, E, just makes his decision, to become a great Hunter.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Released by DATA EAST in Japan in 1991, Metal Max was one of the more "creative" role-playing games amongst 
	[a class=extlink href=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Console_role-playing_game rel=nofollow 
		"Console RPGs
	]a
	", due to more freedom on the story. The game is set in a 
	[a class=extlink href=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Post-apocalyptic rel=nofollow 
		"post-apocalyptic
	]a
	" future, in which surviving people cluster from villages to ruins, while some Hunters from them fight monsters and outlaws in the "wild".
	$LF
]p
